# #Misfits Change - HL2 Combine Department Locale

## Department Names
department-CivilProtection = Civil Protection
department-TranshumanArm = Transhuman Arm
department-Overwatch = Overwatch
department-Logistics = Maintenance & Logistics
department-CivilServices = Civil Services
department-Resistance = Resistance

## Department Descriptions
department-CivilProtection-description = The Civil Protection division maintains order among the civilian population. They are the public face of Combine authority, enforcing curfews, managing checkpoints, and suppressing dissent.
department-TranshumanArm-description = The Transhuman Arm consists of genetically and cybernetically enhanced soldiers. They are the Combine's elite military force, deployed for major operations and suppression of organized resistance.
department-Overwatch-description = Overwatch is the administrative and surveillance branch. They coordinate city operations, monitor civilian activity, and maintain communication with the Universal Union.
department-Logistics-description = Maintenance and logistics keeps the city running. They repair infrastructure, manage supply chains, and operate the rail network that connects Combine facilities.
department-CivilServices-description = Civil services are the essential roles that keep the civilian population functional — medical care, public works, and a facade of normal governance.
department-Resistance-description = The Lambda Resistance operates in the shadows, fighting against Combine occupation. Members risk summary execution if discovered.

