## Job Descriptions
job-description-cpofficer = Maintain order in the city. Patrol the streets, man checkpoints, enforce Combine law. Report suspicious activity to Overwatch.
job-description-cpsergeant = Lead a squad of Civil Protection officers. Coordinate responses to civil disturbances and ensure your officers follow protocol.
job-description-cpcaptain = Command the Civil Protection forces in your sector. Report directly to Overwatch administration.
job-description-ovwatch-officer = Monitor Civil Protection for compliance. Report internal breaches and ensure loyalty to the Universal Union.

job-description-combine-soldier = You are the fist of the Universal Union. Deploy to neutralize threats that exceed Civil Protection capabilities.
job-description-elite-soldier = An enhanced transhuman warrior. You lead critical assaults and guard high-value Combine assets.
job-description-hunter-seeker = Operate and maintain Combine Hunter-Synth units and surveillance drones. Support ground forces from a technical vantage.

job-description-ovwatch-admin = Oversee city administration for the Universal Union. Manage resource allocation and approve major operations.
job-description-ovatch-operator = Interface with the Overwatch AI network. Monitor city-wide surveillance and coordinate response to Lambda activity.

job-description-maintenance = Keep Combine infrastructure operational. Repair damage, maintain power grids, and support facility operations.
job-description-logistics = Manage supply chains and resource distribution. Ensure Civil Protection and Combine forces receive necessary equipment.
job-description-train-yard = Operate the rail network connecting Combine facilities. Transport personnel, supplies, and equipment across the city.

job-description-civil-worker = Perform essential public works — street cleaning, rubble clearing, basic repairs. Your labor keeps the city functioning.
job-description-civil-medic = Provide basic medical care to the civilian population. Your clinic is underfunded and monitored by Civil Protection.
job-description-union-rep = Act as a liaison between the civilian population and the Combine administration. A dangerous position that requires careful diplomacy.

job-description-citizen = You are a resident of the city. Follow Combine regulations, report for civil assignments, and try to survive.
job-description-refugee = Recently arrived in the city after displacement. You have nothing but the clothes on your back and must find your place.

job-description-lambda-cell = You are a member of the Lambda Resistance. Gather intelligence, recruit sympathizers, and sabotage Combine operations.
job-description-resistance-scout = Move unseen through the city. Map Combine positions, identify weak points, and relay information to Lambda command.
job-description-lambda-leader = Command a Lambda Resistance cell. Plan operations, manage resources, and keep your operatives alive in the fight against the Combine.
